{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were separated from them by wire and we were not supposed to speak to them, but we still managed to speak to them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I-- I remained in a flannel-- sleeveless, flannel shirt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was still snowing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Barefoot, sleeveless, flannel shirt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was all that I had on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And one of the Frenchmen gave me one of his jackets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was rather threadbare, but at least covered me a little bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He also gave me a piece of soap and we spoke a few times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I don't remember how many days we were there exactly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I know-- well, it would have been six days, I think so, because I know that we-- on the 13th we were put onto the road-- 12th or 13th we were put onto the road for our death march.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And for the next ten days we were on our death march.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were 15,000 men and women, and at every stop this man who gave me my jacket and my soap would come up, and he was weaker and weaker.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And after about four days he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He didn't come anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I didn't see him anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This is a very important point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then he-- then we went-- we dragged ourselves on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And some people managed to escape when we got to a forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Luciana and four other friends of mine, my closest friends, escaped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then we heard shots from the forest and the SS said, well, they have been found and they have been shot, which wasn't true, luckily.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But I-- I dragged on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- And I dragged on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we were taken to-- they told us they are taking us towards Dresden and over the Elba.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
